create(address,address).details: Creates a Timeswap V2 Option based on pair parameters.Cannot create a duplicate Timeswap V2 Option with the same pair parameters.

params.optionPair: The address of the Timeswap V2 Option contract created.
params.token0: The first ERC20 token address of the pair.
params.token1: The second ERC20 token address of the pair.

get(address,address).details: Returns the address of a Timeswap V2 Option.Returns a zero address if the Timeswap V2 Option does not exist.

params.token0: The first ERC20 token address of the pair.
params.token1: The second ERC20 token address of the pair.

returns.optionPair: The address of the Timeswap V2 Option contract or a zero address.

numberOfPairs().details: The number of option pairs deployed.

create(address,address).notice: The token0 address must be smaller than token1 address.

get(address,address).notice: The token0 address must be smaller than token1 address.

parameter().notice: Get the parameters to be used in constructing the pair, set transiently during pair creation.
